defaultAbout Brdefaultookdefault&#xa0;defaultBrook is the UK’s leading provider of sexual health services and advice for young people under 25. Our mission is to ensure young people can enjoy their sexuality without harm.
default defaultBrook services provide free and confidential sexual health information, co
defaultntraception, pregnancy testing, advice and counselling, testing and treatment for sexually transmitted infections and outreach and education work, reaching over 290,000 young people every year. 
