defaultBrook believes that every young person in Britain deserves 
defaultsex and relationships education (SRE) that is relevant to them, focuses on relationships as well as sex, honest about human sexuality and taught by professionals who are well prepared and confident. Sex and relationships are a life skill, as important to o
defaultur future health and happiness as any other subject, and young people deserve to be heard.
