defaultSex and Relationship Education Guidance
default 
default(2000). This guidance 
defaultpre-dates the Sexual Offences Act 2003, the repeal of Section 28 of the Local Government Act and the 2010 Equalities legislation which includes the recommendation that schools teach gender equality and non-violent, respectful relationships between women an
defaultd men.
default&#xa0;
default This current Government SRE guidance also pre-dates recent and emerging issues on technology and safeguarding, with no reference to addressing on-line safety, '
defaultsexting
