default“Educate the parents, who can in turn educate the children.” 
defaultYoung person, 18.
default&#xa0;
defaultTo enable parents to act accordingly, they suggested that education should be provided to parents so that they are able to understand and set parental controls. The young people we spoke to all knew how to do this themselves, describing 
defaultthe process as simple, and felt that there should be no reason why children should see adult content if they don't want to. 
