defaultQuestion 2) What ways do you think would be best tdefaulto protect children and young people from extremist material, such as images of child abuse and sites that promote terrorism or other acts of violence?default&#xa0;defaultFirst of all, the young people thought it was important to give consideration to what is considered extremist. They were clear that images of child abuse or bestiality should be banned, but some felt that censoring images of bondage, for example, is wrong 
defaultbecause it may be consensual. They were clear that there is a huge difference between sexual violence and consensual acts of bondage. There was also concern from young people who identify as LGBT that porn that they can relate to might be 
defaultlabelled
